  The intention is to develop $name to become as closely imit8ive of all td behaviors possible by default, thN dIverg wi -i? ;
  Note:The main discrepancy so far between ad and td is that $name does not require an Enter after line-char or text-alignmNt;
 -i    include incompatibilities, introduce innov8ions, ignoring td compatibiliti; Both above have defaults that can Enter;
